                     <interp inst="t18470614-1529-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 1 bag, value 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 1 half-sovereign, 1 sixpence, and 3 pence; the property of <persName id="t18470614-name-1103" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18470614-name-1103" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470614-name-1103" type="surname" value="PAYNE"></interp>
